
=============
Prerequisites
=============

The unisync server depends on these programs. Make sure that they are
installed prior to installing the client.

- Bash
- Lsyncd (Version 2.0.7 or later)
- Unison

============
Installation
============

If you pulled the source from git, run autogen:

./autogen.sh

To install the server, execute the following in the root directory of
the code:

./configure
make
su -c 'make install'

The server is now installed. You can run it with the unisync-server
command.